{"tid":1709853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動一定要持續","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T11:05:42.000Z","uid":61886,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a302b11d247fcdc78e472ccb330c37aff5b947c7","tid":1709853,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"1. 延長狗仔出動時間<br />\n之前一至五就最多夜晚先要出動<br />\n而家就由朝做到晚<br />\n<br />\n2. 示威輪更制<br />\n要明白好多人都罷唔到工<br />\n所以而家就會係朝早主要由學生開始<br />\n中午lunch time各大商業區打工仔接力<br />\nlunch time後學生再進場<br />\n夜晚上班人士放工後再接力<br />\n學生就早睡早起 聽朝繼續<br />\n<br />\n3. 一至五朝早係春袋<br />\n平時夜晚或者星期六日金鐘任你玩<br />\n因為經濟影響太細<br />\n而家直擊經濟春袋<br />\n尋日中環5點幾已經死城咁<br />\n<br />\n各位手足<br />\n謹記 最重要係不被捕 不流血"},{"pid":"90c09e7ac26218de461656aeac732a5ea5416fec","tid":1709853,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:06:28.000Z","msg":"但最重要係<br />\n事不過三<br />\n每日都要改變策略<br />\n唔係就好易被狗咬"},{"pid":"e97c6e6e92549ab5097c2d8e326759963a239d53","tid":1709853,"uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"次次d行動有成效<br />\n就有班休息師出場<br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"f11f145b8a63cc654a916ba9fc53dc01c7e43a97","tid":1709853,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47cd26eb5fb770e9821dd5780fe9ed87ec1e915","tid":1709853,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98962619d4b5170443487dd9d57a53bc7cf13b14","tid":1709853,"uid":26101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"日日都三罷就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72afe9da5dd14adba09ce442ddfd038253721571","tid":1709853,"uid":321606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"確實做到班人已經發瘋...... 依家淩晨 1 點後 無出黎趕, 明顯唔夠人......."},{"pid":"c356ebee304606ff533c914dc15e3efbb6440a16","tid":1709853,"uid"